  fullBackstory: "Ge\xE7mi\u015F: \xD6nceki hayat\u0131nda \xC7in'de ya\u015Fayan
    s\u0131radan bir kurba\u011Fa.\n\r\n\xD6l\xFCm \u015Fekli: \u0130\xE7inde torpil
    patlam\u0131\u015F...\n\r\nSon s\xF6z\xFC: \"WRAAKKKKKKKK!!!\""
  soulCoins: 0
  dialogueLines:
  - text: "Mewhaba, wrak \u2014 a, pardon. "
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: -4825247317447833179, guid: bf2f3b44877b98849a8e1c463dee7f61, type: 3}
  - text: "\u015Eey, reenkarne olmaya geldim de... iiii, m\xFCmk\xFCnse \xC7in olmas\u0131n..."
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: 9103029724409692841, guid: 8e0927f7fd569e74f813d62da09f06c5, type: 3}
  - text: "\xC7inli \xE7ocuklardan nefret ediyorum..."
    emotion: 1
    expression: {fileID: -7442742369925825077, guid: bdef9e4cb7049da4ebabbcb39f987426, type: 3}
